        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Shall serve me - Shall worship me, or be regarded as my people.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In this place - That is, in the place where God made this promise to Abraham. These words are not found in Genesis, but similar words are found in Exodus 3:12, and it was a practice, in making quotations, to quote the sense only, or to connect two or more promises having relation to the same thing. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "In this place - That is, in the place where God made this promise to Abraham. These words are not found in Genesis, but similar words are found in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Exodus 3:12",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", and it was a practice, in making quotations, to quote the sense only, or to connect two or more promises having relation to the same thing. ",
