        "text": "and serve me in this place; in the land of Canaan; though these words are not to be found in Genesis 15:13 what comes nearest them is in Exodus 3:12. \"Ye shall serve God upon this mountain\"; meaning Mount Horeb, where Moses then was, and from whence the law was afterwards given. ",
